# The per-platform CIRIS Desktop JAR is a CI build artifact, staged here by the
# publish-pypi workflow (gradle :desktopApp:packageUberJarForCurrentOS) right
# before the maturin wheel build. It is NEVER committed (tens of MB; per-OS).
# This directory must exist in git so maturin's python-source package layout is
# present at build time even when no JAR has been staged (headless/source path).
CIRIS-*.jar
